\f0 \cf0 Yes. Rhythm Ribbon is close conceptually, but it can be tuned to feel more like those video references: rounded bar caps/sides, stronger frequency-driven height changes, and more obvious mid/high movement through the band. I\'92ll adjust that style without touching your favorite existing ones.
\f3 \
\

\f0 I\'92m also going to keep the \'93striped\'94 character, but thicken it slightly so the rounded sides register instead of looking like square ticks.
\f3 \
\

\f0 The Rhythm Ribbon is currently made from thin rectangular slices. I\'92m going to switch those to rounded vertical capsules and raise the frequency contribution so peaks breathe more visibly across the band.
\f3 \
\
\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

